OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Gas suspends       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fforce-fitting prepay meters
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Gas has suspended the          
OL,6, force-fitting of prepayment meters,    
OL,7, after a report said it imposed them on 
OL,8, vulnerable customers.                  
OL,10,FThe Times reported a company employed  
OL,11,Fby British Gas broke into homes to fit 
OL,12,Fthe meters, despite signs that children
OL,13,Fand disabled people were living there. 
OL,15,FBusiness Secretary Grant Shapps said he
OL,16,Fwas "horrified" by the findings.       
OL,18,FBritish Gas's owner Centrica said it   
OL,19,Fwould suspend the use of court warrants
OL,20,Fthat allow forced installations.       
